  "text": "According to our knowledge, there are only 12 cases reported in the literature [ Table 1 ]. A history of previous pancreatic surgery or stenting is frequently reported. [CITATION_1] Unfortunately, the diagnosis is often made after the surgery when medical therapy is the only treatment required.",
